org.hl7.fhir.instance.model

Class Composition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Base
      • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.BaseResource
        • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Resource
          • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.DomainResource
            • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Composition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IAnyResource, IBase, IBaseHasExtensions, IBaseHasModifierExtensions, IBaseResource, IDomainResource

    public class Composition
extends DomainResource
    A set of healthcare-related information that is assembled together into a single logical document that provides a single coherent statement of meaning, establishes its own context and that has clinical attestation with regard to who is making the statement.
